# Privacy Policy

Last updated: 5/17/2025

BerryBreach (“we”, “us”, or “our”) is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your information when you use our application.

## Information We Collect

- **Account Information:** We collect your Discord user ID and basic profile information for authentication.
- **Payment Information:** Payments are processed securely via Stripe. We do not store your credit card details.
- **Usage Data:** We may collect anonymized usage data to improve our service and prevent abuse.

## How We Use Your Information

- To authenticate users and manage account access
- To process payments and manage credits
- To provide and improve our services
- To comply with legal obligations

## Data Sharing

- We do not sell or share your personal information with third parties, except as required by law or to process payments (via Stripe).

## Data Security

- We use industry-standard security measures to protect your data.

## Your Rights

- You may request deletion of your account and associated data at any time by contacting us.

## Contact Us

If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at glvckoma on discord or our server at https://discord.gg/skWwUwaTsp
